      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KALANI CRUISE (4) was in the money again last start when second at The Gardens (29.89). Good beginner who will be prominent from trap seven. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. MR. ALEXANDER (5) is a solid beginner and with a good start can clear the draw. Latest effort finished 3rd on February 19 over 520m at this track behind Zipping Kayli beaten 13 lengths (30.54) in a Maiden. Looks a key player on best form. RITZA BOB (2) recorded his best time this course and distance latest, finishing a 10 length third behind Extreme Machine in 30.71. Has the ability and looks a key chance. STILL SHADY (8) cannot be underestimated.",
